    "more": "<div style='padding-bottom: 10px; font-size: 2em; font-weight: bold; line-height: 1.2em; text-align: center;'>Information:</div><p style='line-height: 1.35em; font-size: 17.5px'><b>This is an algorithmically generated map of Persian Twitch</b><ul style='font-size: 1.25em;margin-left: 15px; padding-bottom: 5px; line-height: 1.5em; font-size: 1.4em; list-style-type: circle;'><li>Generally, this map represents the behavior of viewers.</li><li>Each bubble is a Twitch channel.</li><li>Each edge represents the overlap of viewers between those two channels.</li><li>Different communities were detected with the Modularity algorithm using Gephi.</li></ul><br><p style='font-size: 17.5px; line-height: 1.35em;'><br>Different parts of this project was made using: <a href='https://gephi.org/'>Gephi</a>, <a href='http://sigmajs.org/'>SigmaJS</a> and <a href='https://dev.twitch.tv/docs/api/'>Twitch API</a>.</p><br>contact me at <a href='https://discord.com/users/500699685137154053'>discord</a></p>",
